Description_lang: Healing an ally below $s4% health grants them Blossom of Amirdrassil, healing for ${$s1*$426678d} over $426678d. This effect may occur once per minute. If the target is above $s5% health when this effect expires, the Blossom spreads to 3 injured allies to heal for ${$s3*$426718d} over $426718d. If the target is not fully healed, the Blossom blooms to absorb $s2 damage instead.
